{"id":72911,"date":"2022-01-24T18:14:25","date_gmt":"2022-01-24T17:14:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=72911"},"modified":"2022-08-12T10:15:07","modified_gmt":"2022-08-12T08:15:07","slug":"la-fortuna","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/la-fortuna\/","title":{"rendered":"8 Best Things to do in La Fortuna, Costa Rica"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in La Fortuna, Costa Rica<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>La Fortuna is perfect for nature lovers and thrill-seekers. Every adventure activity you can imagine is available here, whether it&#x2019;s horseback riding, ziplining, tubing, canyoning, or white water rafting. Use these methods of travel to discover tropical wildlife, excellent birdwatching, and luscious landscapes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"la fortuna best things to do costa rica volcano\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"323\" alt=\"la fortuna best things to do costa rica volcano\" class=\"wp-image-74336 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-800x575.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-1080x776.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-450x323.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-163x117.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-250x180.jpg 250w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-768x552.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-1024x736.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-1440x1035.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-300x216.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-600x431.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1-30x22.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23173435\/la-fortuna-2-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-1-la-fortuna-waterfall\">1. La Fortuna Waterfall&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>La Fortuna Waterfall sits just outside town and is popular with travelers and locals looking to cool off in the impressive natural pools. Hike for around 30 minutes down steep stairs (about 600!), through the stunning green rainforest, before reaching the base of the mighty waterfall. The powerful waterfall plummets to the natural pool below from a height of 70 meters. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/costa-rica-itinerary-7-days\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Complete 7-day Costa Rica Itinerary<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2.jpg\" alt=\"la fortuna waterfall \"><\/noscript><img width=\"238\" height=\"338\" alt=\"la fortuna waterfall \" class=\"wp-image-73886 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1353px) 100vw, 1353px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2.jpg 1353w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-423x600.jpg 423w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-571x810.jpg 571w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-238x338.jpg 238w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-115x163.jpg 115w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-127x180.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-541x768.jpg 541w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162916\/la-fortuna-2-722x1024.jpg 722w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/0