 The money is also invested in the park to improve infrastructure and environmental conservation.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"la fortuna waterfall things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"la fortuna waterfall things to do\" class=\"wp-image-74144 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21233253\/la-fortuna-waterfall-2-300x450.jpg