, into the refreshing pool. It&#x2019;s the perfect place to cool off and enjoy nature as you relax and sunbathe on the surrounding rocks. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Also visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Monteverde Cloud Forest in Costa Rica<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21225732\/la-fortuna-el-salto.jpg\" alt=\"la fortuna things to do el salto\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"la fortuna things to do el salto\" class=\"wp-image-74141 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21225732\/la-fortuna-el-salto.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21225732\/la-fortuna-el-salto-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21225732\/la-fortuna-el-salto-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21225732\/la-fortuna-el-salto-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21225732\/la-fortuna-el-salto-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21225732\/la-fortuna-el-salto-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/21225732\/la