div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-the-arenal-1968-route\">The Arenal 1968 Route<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Head for the Arenal 1968 section of the park, where you&#x2019;ll find two paths to choose from (there is a network of trails you can find in other areas of the park, too) that snake through the rainforest. Follow signs and take the two-hour walk to the volcano viewpoint.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23045335\/la-fortuna-arenal-volcano-3-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"la fortuna arenal volcano hike \"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"la fortuna arenal volcano hike \" class=\"wp-image-74313 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23045335\/la-fortuna-arenal-volcano-3-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23045335\/la-fortuna-arenal-volcano-3-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23045335\/la-fortuna-arenal-volcano-3-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23045335\/la-fortuna-arenal-volcano-3-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23045335\/la-fortuna-arenal-volcano-3-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23045335\/la-fortuna-arenal-volcano-3-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23045335\/la-fortuna-arenal-volcano-3-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23045335\/la-fortuna-arenal-volcano-3-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltino