911&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24180027\/La-fortuna-costa-rica-2.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24180027\/La-fortuna-costa-rica-2-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/24180027\/La-fortuna-costa-rica-2-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"8 Best Things to do in La Fortuna, Costa Rica\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-4-hot-springs-la-fortuna\">4. Hot Springs, La Fortuna<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The active volcano in La Fortuna makes it a hotspot for geothermal activity. This means there are lots of Hot Springs in La Fortuna to choose from, all of which are between a comfortable 35-38 degrees. Generally, these springs are attached to hotels, so you have to pay for a day pass or stay at the hotel to access them. However, there are hot springs in La Fortuna for all budgets and even some free ones!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Also discover the incredible <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/puerto-viejo\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Caribbean town Puerto Viejo<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19182141\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-5.jpg\" alt=\"tabacon hot spring la fortuna costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"tabacon hot spring la fortuna costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-73950 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19182141\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-5.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19182141\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-5-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19182141\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-5-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19182141\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-5-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19182141\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-5-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19182141\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-5-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19182141\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-5-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19182141\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-5-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/202