"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Please note:<\/strong> You can only pay by card for these hot springs in La Fortuna. <a href=\"#budget\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Read our best budget saving tip here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s worth checking the price of staying at Tabacon Resort overnight. Sometimes, staying for the night is not much more than the day pass; a lovely luxury treat on your trip!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173911\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-3.jpg\" alt=\"la fortuna hot springs\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"323\" alt=\"la fortuna hot springs\" class=\"wp-image-73920 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173911\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-3.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173911\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-3-800x574.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173911\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-3-1080x775.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173911\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-3-450x323.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173911\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-3-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173911\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-3-163x117.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173911\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-3-251x180.jpg 251w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19173911\/la-fortuna-hotsprings-3-768x551.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.