hair.com\/costa-rica\/rio-celeste-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Rio Celeste<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/rio-celeste-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Rio Celeste<\/a> is a beautiful nature spot about 1.5 hours away from La Fortuna, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Costa Rica<\/a>, in the Tenorio Volcano National Park. Although it&#x2019;s a little remote and hard to get to, it&#x2019;s totally worth it when you first see the incredible blue waterfall plummeting into the pools below.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/rio-celeste-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Read everything about the Rio Celeste Waterfalls<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162524\/la-fortuna-1.jpg\" alt=\"la fortuna costa rica Rio celeste waterfall\"><\/noscript><img width=\"262\" height=\"338\" alt=\"la fortuna costa rica Rio celeste waterfall\" class=\"wp-image-73881 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1490px) 100vw, 1490px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162524\/la-fortuna-1.jpg 1490w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19162524\/la-fortuna-1-466x600.jp