"noreferrer noopener\">Book your canyoning tour here<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/lafortuna-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Here are all your hotel options in La Fortuna<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-8-mistico-arenal-hanging-bridges\">8. Mistico Arenal Hanging Bridges<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Mistico Arenal Hanging Bridges are a bucket list thing to do in La Fortuna. Discover the unique hanging bridges suspended among the rainforest canopy as you walk among amazing animals like sloths, tarantulas, and frogs. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As you walk, take the time to look down onto the stunning forest from the incredible height of 45 meters (or 148 feet)! Floating among the treetops, listening to the peaceful sounds of wildlife around you is truly an experience like no other. (For more wildlife visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Manuel Antonio National Park<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170805\/la-fortuna-Mistico-2-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Mistico Arenal Hanging Bridges  la fortuna\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Mistico Arena