pe\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>Come in the morning, as this time usually is quieter and the weather is often better. Don&#x2019;t forget to wear closed-toe shoes as the trail can be muddy, and there are lots of creepy crawlies around!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170818\/la-fortuna-Mistico-3-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"toucan costa rica \"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"toucan costa rica \" class=\"wp-image-73892 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170818\/la-fortuna-Mistico-3-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170818\/la-fortuna-Mistico-3-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170818\/la-fortuna-Mistico-3-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170818\/la-fortuna-Mistico-3-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170818\/la-fortuna-Mistico-3-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170818\/la-fortuna-Mistico-3-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170818\/la-fortuna-Mistico-3-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170818\/la-fortuna-Mistico-3-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/19170818\/la-fortuna-Mistico-3-721x1080.jpg 721w